程序包 hdb.data.relational

类 Tuple

java.lang.Object
hdb.data.relational.Tuple
所有已实现的接口:
java.io.Serializable
public class Tuple
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
A Tuple represents a record in a relation containing a number of attributes.
作者:
Jeong-Hyon Hwang (jhh@cs.albany.edu)

  • 构造器详细资料

    • Tuple

      public Tuple​(RelationSchema schema, java.lang.Object... attributeValues) throws Tuple.TypeException
      Constructs a Tuple.
      参数:
      schema - a RelationSchema
      attributeValues - the attribute values of the Tuple
      抛出:
      Tuple.TypeException - if a specified attribute value does not match the type of the corresponding attribute

    • Tuple

      public Tuple​(RelationSchema schema, java.io.ObjectInputStream in) throws java.lang.ClassNotFoundException, Tuple.TypeException, java.io.IOException, RelationSchema.InvalidAttributeIndexException
      Constructs a Tuple from the specified ObjectInputStream.
      参数:
      schema - a RelationSchema
      in - an ObjectInputStream
      抛出:
      Tuple.TypeException - if an attribute value does not match the type of the corresponding attribute
      java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs
      java.lang.ClassNotFoundException - if the class of a serialized object cannot be found
      RelationSchema.InvalidAttributeIndexException - if an invalid attribute index is given

      Sets the value of the specified attribute.
